A new program for 13–17 year olds, Neo is proudly presented by the Balnaves Foundation.&nbsp;

'Neo' means new, youthful, fresh, lately and now. It suggests the spirit of the contemporary, so it is an ideal name for the Gallery's program of activities and talks led by artists and art lovers just for teen audiences.&nbsp;

Neo Nights pays homage to the contemporary in August with a dynamic program of activities, art and ideas for teens inspired by the work of South Australia’s living artists.&nbsp;

Neo Nights is presented free thanks to The Balnaves Foundation.&nbsp;

Amazing India&nbsp;is&nbsp;A local artists’ production that takes you through a journey of Indian classical, contemporary, folk as well as Bollywood songs and dances presented by Kalalaya School of Indian Performing Arts.

